UPDATE public.provider_tests SET description = 'This test is the UK''s most comprehensive allergy panel with 295 allergens tested. Utilising innovative microarray technology it analyses the widest range of allergens available in any profile - all with one blood sample. The sample can even be a finger-prick home kit, which is a remarkable advance in technology.' WHERE id = '9cfd0094-47b0-445e-9f75-e4e682ad22de';

UPDATE public.provider_tests SET description = 'This comprehensive profile analyses 7 parameters including total cholesterol, triglycerides, HDL (good) and LDL (bad) levels, plus the ratios between them. Over 40% of UK adults have raised cholesterol — a significant risk factor for heart attacks and strokes — and a blood test is the only reliable way to know your levels.' WHERE id = '9fd98cee-91a2-4429-82c1-4c7def8541e0';

UPDATE public.provider_tests SET description = 'Undiagnosed, untreated diabetes can significantly shorten life expectancy and reduce quality of life. Diabetes leads to excess glucose in the blood, which damages small blood vessels and, over time, virtually every organ and system in the body. This HbA1c test reflects average blood sugar over the previous 2–3 months.' WHERE id = '28dd5aa7-9471-4a04-b16d-0f15a217952b';

UPDATE public.provider_tests SET description = 'This comprehensive profile checks the health indicators that can contribute to erectile dysfunction and male impotence. It is estimated that around 48% of men experience difficulty getting or maintaining an erection on at least some occasions, and underlying hormonal, cardiovascular or metabolic factors are often involved.' WHERE id = 'e8cff3a0-1cb3-45b2-9481-304c8c6ed6b3';

UPDATE public.provider_tests SET description = 'Hair loss in women can be driven by a complex mix of hormonal imbalances, thyroid dysfunction, nutritional deficiencies and chronic stress. The Female Hair Loss Advanced profile is designed to help uncover what is happening internally by analysing key biomarkers linked to hair health, growth and vitality.' WHERE id = '1c005c39-e43f-405b-8016-080e9e29e68d';